Package project.star_wars_universe.util.comparators

package project.star_wars_universe.util.comparators
Contains classes that implement the Comparator interface and are used by various other classes (such as Collections and TreeSet) for sorting sets of data by different criteria.

  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    JediByAgeAndName
    A Comparator implementation which imposes an order based on the Jedi.age field first (ascending) and the Jedi.name field second (lexicographically, ascending) on a collection of Jedi.
    JediByName
    A Comparator implementation which imposes an order based on the Jedi.name field on a collection of Jedi.
    JediByRankAndName
    A Comparator implementation which imposes an order based on the Jedi.rank field first (ascending) and the Jedi.name field second (lexicographically, ascending) on a collection of Jedi.
    JediByStrength
    A Comparator implementation which imposes an order based on the Jedi.power field on a collection of Jedi.
